79
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:34,699
And in the days of the Roman Republic, they
hated you.

80
00:04:34,699 --> 00:04:38,560
They thought you barbarous.
They thought that people wearing you was

81
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:42,160
the definition of people lacking civilization.

82
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:45,560
They ventured north and the wind blew up through
